Thanks for downloading and playing!
Map made by: Ivar van Wooning
Sponsored by: Black-IRC.eu

Check other maps of me: breakfloor_missgreece, ka_delta_knifefight!

STORY: You spawn with nothing, so you have to pickup a knife, in the weapon_dispencer.
Then move to the cable-way and go to the platform, now the fight starts. with only knifes! But(!), it's not as easy
as you think! If someone steps in the caution strips, he will die immediately! So: fight for your life, and thanks
for playing.

Ivar
